text: The material relating to the TE/GE Records Control Schedule previously contained in IRM 1.15.24 was incorporated into the November 2017 revision of Document 12990, Records and Information Management Records Control Schedules.
IRM 1.15.24, dated September 21, 2015 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
